These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, martial-arts, epic
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left##1
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | epic | sports |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-2::.
There are 3 different nationalities: british, brazilian, french
1. the french is on the far right##1
2. the british is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1    |   2    |      3       |
| Nationality   | british | brazilian | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, dahlia, bellflower
1. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
2. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |    2    |      3      |
| Flower   | azalea | dahlia | bellflower |

